BADWORDS:

(eger BLOCKBADWORDS ayarlanmissa) kanalda yazilan kelimeleri
badwords listesindekilerle eslestirmeye calisir.

Eylem parametreleri: KICK, WARN, BAN, KICKBAN ya da (IRCdiniz
destekliyorsa) QUIET

Sentaks: BADWORDS <#kanal> LIST
Sentaks: BADWORDS <#kanal> ADD <kelime> <eylem>
Sentaks: BADWORDS <#kanal> DEL <kelime>

Kullanimi:
    /msg &nick& BADWORDS #atheme LIST
    /msg &nick& BADWORDS #sailors ADD f?ck kick
    /msg &nick& BADWORDS #sailors ADD *dam?it* quiet
    /msg &nick& BADWORDS #desensitized DEL f?ck
